title: Prince & The Revolution - Parade (1986) - FLAC - MP3 - Fuzzy
description:
This is an amateur "remaster" of Prince & The Revolution's 1986 album, Parade.

The music files contained within this upload, have been sourced from the regular Compact Discs that we all purchased at the time of original release. No Hi-Res formats or SHM-CD rips have been used.

Instead, a series of minor EQ adjustments and digital filters have been utilised, to increase the bass, brighten the treble, and maximise the overall loudness of the audio from the original Compact Discs.

Hearing is very subjective, but I hope you enjoy these "tweaked" files, until (hopefully) officially-released professional remasters are available to buy.

Try downloading a couple of the MP3 files from the torrent first, and then if you like what you hear, grab the FLAC too
